cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL 

This paper deals with training CNN models for action recognition in videos using web action images. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) likely sub-categories. The paper also involves information retrieval techniques for collecting web images, which makes cs.IR (Information Retrieval) a possible sub-category. Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for filtering web images, which makes cs.CL (Computation and Language) a possible sub-category.
